Class MCMCFileReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.cbb.jprime.apps.vmcmc.libs.MCMCFileReader

  • public abstract class MCMCFileReader
extends java.lang.Object
    MCMCFileReader: Static class responsible for handling files. Interprets files of formats (.mcmc) and stores the results as a MCMCDataContainer. Class containins static methods for converting byte arrays to appropriate datastructures.
